"title": "5042: name of God, significance of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5042",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>God's name is synonymous with his person, his presence and his power, and is therefore held in the highest honour.</p>\n<h2>God is referred to as the Name</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:41\">ACT 5:41</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev24:10-Lev24:16\">LEV 24:10–24:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam6:2\">2SA 6:2</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr13:6\">1CH 13:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/3John1:7\">3JN 1:7</a></p>\n<h2>God's person is revealed in his name</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:5-Exod34:7\">EXO 34:5–34:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen14:18-Gen14:20\">GEN 14:18–14:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen17:1\">GEN 17:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen21:33\">GEN 21:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen32:29-Gen32:30\">GEN 32:29–32:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod3:13-Exod3:15\">EXO 3:13–3:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod6:3\">EXO 6:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:19\">EXO 33:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg13:17-Judg13:18\">JDG 13:17–13:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer16:21\">JER 16:21</a></p>\n<h2>God's name is synonymous with his presence</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num6:22-Num6:27\">NUM 6:22–6:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut12:5-Deut12:7\">DEU 12:5–12:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:15-1Kgs8:21\">1KI 8:15–8:21</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr6:4-2Chr6:11\">2CH 6:4–6:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh1:9\">NEH 1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps20:1\">PSA 20:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps54:1\">PSA 54:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps74:7\">PSA 74:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps75:1\">PSA 75:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:27\">ISA 30:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:11-John17:12\">JHN 17:11–17:12</a></p>\n<h2>The name of God identifies his people</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:10\">DEU 28:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr7:14\">2CH 7:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa43:6-Isa43:7\">ISA 43:6–43:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic4:5\">MIC 4:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic5:4\">MIC 5:4</a></p>\n<h2>Dishonouring God's name is a serious offence</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:7\">EXO 20:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:12\">LEV 19:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev22:2\">LEV 22:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev22:32\">LEV 22:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps74:10\">PSA 74:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps74:18\">PSA 74:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps139:20\">PSA 139:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek43:7-Ezek43:8\">EZK 43:7–43:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal1:6\">MAL 1:6</a></p>\n<h2>The righteous honour God's name</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps29:2\">PSA 29:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh1:11\">NEH 1:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps86:11-Ps86:12\">PSA 86:11–86:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:13\">ISA 26:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal2:5\">MAL 2:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:16-Mal4:2\">MAL 3:16–4:2</a></p>\n<h2>The name of Jesus Christ</h2>\n<h3>Supplication is to be made in the name of Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:13-John14:14\">JHN 14:13–14:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:19-Matt18:20\">MAT 18:19–18:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:16\">JHN 15:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:23-John16:24\">JHN 16:23–16:24</a></p>\n<h3>Healing and other miracles performed in the name of Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:6-Acts3:8\">ACT 3:6–3:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:16\">ACT 3:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:30\">ACT 4:30</a></p>\n<h3>Baptism is in Jesus Christ's name</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:38\">ACT 2:38</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:19\">MAT 28:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:12\">ACT 8:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:15-Acts8:16\">ACT 8:15–8:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:48\">ACT 10:48</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:5\">ACT 19:5</a></p>\n<h3>Salvation is in the name of Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:12\">ACT 4:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:6\">JHN 14:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:31\">JHN 20:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:21\">ACT 2:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:32\">JOL 2:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:11\">1CO 6:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:12\">1JN 2:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:9-Phil2:11\">PHP 2:9–2:11</a></p>",
